The path included in the body is sanitized.

    >>> print app.get('/<b>hi</b>', status=404).body
    <html>
    <head><title>Not Found</title></head>
    <body>Could not find: /%3Cb%3Ehi%3C/b%3E</body>
    </html>
    <BLANKLINE>

